{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"auto","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Case","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@E@SBSDKProcessingMode@SBSDKProcessingModeAuto","symbolKind":"case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKProcessingModeAuto","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"SBSDKProcessingMode.auto"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKProcessingMode"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKProcessingMode\/auto"},"abstract":[{"text":"The scanner chooses live or single-shot mode based on the source of the image. An image constructed with RawImageLoadOptions.liveSource equal to true will be processed in live mode, otherwise it will be processed in single-shot mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"On Android liveSource is automatically set to true if the ImageRef is created from Nv21 image data.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"On iOS liveSource is automatically set to true if the ImageRef is created from a CMSampleBuffer.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkprocessingmode\/auto"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkprocessingmode\/auto"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"auto"}],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/do